lead_paragraph: The New England Patriots went back to practice without Rob Gronkowski on Friday as the 2015 All-Pro tight end prepared for season-ending back surgery.

headline.print_headline: Brady on Gronk: 'We've Still Got a Lot of Good Players'
headline.main: Brady on Gronk: 'We've Still Got a Lot of Good Players'
